{
  "id": "RAW_6c6b5040",
  "title": "等待 AI 写代码的时候，我该干点什么好？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&mid=2247500022&idx=1&sn=654b269cc2b69de120779b8bb8dc91dd",
  "date": "2025-12-14 16:04:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b21db6cc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVCtjiaeG5ebljN2a4R7Fx0KFicsn8fKlKSovrNgfvYm6TAGEoH9X9E7mdg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">哈喽，大家好，我是刘小排。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">凌晨两点，你的显示器幽幽地发着蓝光。Cursor 的光标在屏幕上疯狂跳动，绿色的代码像瀑布一样流淌。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">你盯着屏幕，双手悬在键盘上方：这120秒，是 Vibe Coding的垃圾时间吗？</span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我想起一个关于张一鸣的轶事。</span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"7\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在字节跳动还只是个雏形，甚至更早他还在写代码的时候，他就在研究一个极其硬核的问题：</span><b><span leaf=\"\">“在程序编译的那10秒钟等待时间里，我到底应该干点什么？”</span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这真是一个伟大的问题！ 当时还没有Vibe Coding呢，现在有了Vibe Coding，恐怕就不是10秒了，而是120秒甚至更久。那时候的代码编译是</span><b data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">物理时间的等待</span></b><span leaf=\"\">，而现在的Vibe Coding，是</span><b><span leaf=\"\">思维的延伸</span></b><span leaf=\"\">。这120秒，决定了你是被AI取代，还是驾驭AI。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面分享一点我会干的事，供你参考。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 21px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: -0.003em;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;margin: 32px 0px !important;color: rgb(36, 36, 36) !important;line-height: 1.58 !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">一、看电子书</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 生成代码的这几分钟，其实是极其宝贵的“高压输入”窗口。这段时间不够你刷完一个抖音视频，但刚好够你读透一个技术概念，或者看一段哲学思考。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这比整块时间阅读更有效。为什么？因为你知道马上就要切回工作，这种</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">倒计时带来的隐形紧迫感</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，会强制你的大脑进入高频吸收状态。这不叫阅读，这叫知识的“静脉注射”。😄</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">看那种书呢？我推荐看可以随时打断的书籍。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如吴军老师的书就很不错，每一篇文章都可以单独看。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">再比如，我最近在重读《论语》。《论语》实际上是孔子和弟子们的微博发言合集，随便看两句都能打断。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016360\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7267015706806282\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1910\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=01a51c5f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVCGPbsFicCwzYQJTtCQ0bXMN8IejxOnXt68z0bHG1Y9RTClwTrVA7QzeA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 21px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: -0.003em;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;margin: 32px 0px !important;color: rgb(36, 36, 36) !important;line-height: 1.58 !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 32px 0px !important; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 36, 36) !important; font-family: -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.003em; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 1.58 !important;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">二、和朋友聊天</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\">有朋友发现我有时候突然微信回消息很频繁，虽然大部分时候都不怎么回。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在我回复比较频繁、话比较多的时候，大概率是我在等待AI写代码、写比较复杂的功能，等待时间较长。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">你如果周围有真实的朋友，而不只是微信，那就更好了</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016369\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7257731958762886\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1940\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6dc5b9db&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVC8evDKoep2ic05oaOVe9xTa0aoMcwurAJ7J3tuGz7jVUic8AEISMYWEpQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">什么？你是说你没有朋友？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">那我推荐你参加我朋友组织的活动，一大群Vibe Coding的人，在咖啡厅一起玩。活动是免费的，你可以看下面的视频了解。</span></p>\n   <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n   <div></div>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 21px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: -0.003em;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;margin: 32px 0px !important;color: rgb(36, 36, 36) !important;line-height: 1.58 !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 32px 0px !important; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 36, 36) !important; font-family: -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.003em; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 1.58 !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 32px 0px !important; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 36, 36) !important; font-family: -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.003em; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 1.58 !important;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">三、写公众号或其他社交媒体</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">一鱼多吃。详细参考<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&amp;mid=2247498295&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b477fc1ee4da8cf25fc28af870eb5205&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"AI时代的人生提效秘籍：时间折叠\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">AI时代的人生提效秘籍：时间折叠</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016362\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5287128712871287\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2020\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5fa94207&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVC3kaEodvyJp1oFM6yYUMlTTgCJG6BR5qEkcd8icAWOLVEYvlC2YePzuQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">再比如，你正在看的这篇公众号。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">自从今年Q2开始更新公众号以来，现在我已经4万多粉丝了，平均每天涨粉200个。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">前几天甚至在AI写代码的间隙尝试了一篇付费文章，竟然3天内卖了超过5万元！我怀疑到月末，这篇能卖10万😂 &nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">既然你这么喜欢我，要不，你也支持一下？👉</span>&nbsp;<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&amp;mid=2247499915&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=3c27ef4939e22a9cf8ac1a8781a79ddf&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"复杂需求如何让AI一次写对？面对复杂需求，这是我实战沉淀的Vibe Coding终极SOP\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">复杂需求如何让AI一次写对？面对复杂需求，这是我实战沉淀的Vibe Coding终极SOP</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你觉得写公众号太重，也可以写Twitter或者其他社交媒体。对了，我的Twitter也一万多粉了，8月才开始做的。</span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://x.com/bourneliu66\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/bourneliu66</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我强烈建议你至少尝试一种社交媒体，因为对于大部分独立开发者来说，Build in Public是一种很好的获取客户、和用户沟通的方式。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">推荐学习张咋啦的这条视频，一条视频就能说服你，为啥Vibe Coding的你一定需要做社交媒体。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\n  <div></div>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 21px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: -0.003em;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;margin: 32px 0px !important;color: rgb(36, 36, 36) !important;line-height: 1.58 !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 32px 0px !important; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 36, 36) !important; font-family: -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.003em; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 1.58 !important;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">四、微运动</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我非常认真！老外也这么玩，</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\">这个流派叫做The \"Micro-Workout\" Tribe（微运动派）。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\">甚至有人在Reddit上还做了脚本，会打开摄像头，监控自己，</span><span leaf=\"\">每次git push或者等待AI生成超过30秒，电脑摄像头就会检测他有没有做深蹲……</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我至少知道三种可以在Vibe Coding运动的方式</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">1. 拉力器</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">2. 划船机</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">3. 走步机办公桌</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我目前用的是前面两个，有同事给我偷偷录下来，做成了表情包……</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016356\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.7714285714285714\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"140\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f3f6711c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVC2MP6GOKdtaRxkziaiavXbeX1t15UQyib5rBv3paAVy1ibicNia6966oNQ5Wg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">至于划船机，我很喜欢，因为它是全身运动。电脑放在划船机旁边，反正是用语音输入，需要输入的时候就暂停一会儿，输入完，马上接着划……</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">可能有点不雅，我就不放视频了哈哈哈哈</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">第三种是我一直考虑的：走步机办公桌。我的计划被同事制止了 —— 他们担心噪音太大，影响他们工作和摸鱼。也许我会考虑在家里买一台。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">虽然同事制止了我，但我其实在想，如果全公司都用走步机，是不是发电量就够跑推理模型了？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016363\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5441767068273092\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1992\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=427a7006&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVCVbyRlk0qY0xKwO2Y7bZRXEm26wyIibWMfpn58QzenuVEStE1OOz7VDQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">做Vibe Coding加微运动，那么语音输入是必须。你可以关注我的公众号，在我公众号回复「<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">输入法</span>」，我给你推荐一款不错的电脑使用的语音输入法、和一款手机使用的语音输入法，两者都是亲测，体验最好的。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n   <p style=\"padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 21px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: -0.003em;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;margin: 32px 0px !important;color: rgb(36, 36, 36) !important;line-height: 1.58 !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 32px 0px !important;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(36, 36, 36) !important;font-family: -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 21px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: -0.003em;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;line-height: 1.58 !important;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">五、干点正事——深度编程</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 []\"><span leaf=\"\">很多人的 Vibe Coding 是线性的：写需求 -&gt; 等生成 -&gt; 报错 -&gt; 再等生成。</span><span leaf=\"\">这种模式下，</span><span leaf=\"\">那 120 秒的等待确实是垃圾时间。</span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><span leaf=\"\">我的玩法是借鉴 CPU 的&nbsp;</span><b><span leaf=\"\">“指令流水线”</span></b><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;技术。</span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><span leaf=\"\">作为一名独立开发者，</span><span leaf=\"\">你必须同时是 PM（产品经理）、</span><span leaf=\"\">Architect（架构师）和 Coder（程序员）。</span><span leaf=\"\">Vibe Coding 的终极奥义，</span><span leaf=\"\">就是利用 AI 生成的间隙，</span><b><span leaf=\"\">在不同维度的身份间快速切换，而不是在不同项目间切换。</span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于新手，尤其是学习期的新手，你可以认真考虑这个方案：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">- 在飞书写需求C</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">- 用Claude Code讨论需求B的技术方案</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">- 用Cursor执行已经充分讨论过技术方案的需求A</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">三线共进，可以利用好所有Vibe Coding的时间，还能深度思考。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016373\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5407035175879397\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1990\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=89f7a993&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVCV3FibqHMApWu6ksEOYiaCdTwhPD1Oot3ibYiatFqLkicRzA0ic9dPnT8Jb6w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><b><span leaf=\"\">再提醒一点：不要横向切换，要纵向切换。</span></b></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"17,0,0\"><b><span leaf=\"\">错误示范</span></b><span leaf=\"\">：Cursor 写项目 A，Claude 聊项目 B，飞书写项目 C。——这会让你大脑“脑裂”（Context Switch Cost 极高），直接宕机。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"17,1,0\"><b><span leaf=\"\">正确姿势</span></b><span leaf=\"\">：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">同一个项目</span>，</span><b><span leaf=\"\">Cursor 写模块 A（现在），Claude 聊模块 B（马上做），飞书定义模块 C（未来做）。</span></b></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">这保持了你对</span><b><span leaf=\"\">同一个产品</span></b><span leaf=\"\">的连贯思考，只是处于不同的</span><b><span leaf=\"\">抽象层级</span></b><span leaf=\"\">（Abstraction Layers）。</span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"19\"><span leaf=\"\">这样一来，你的大脑就像流水线一样，永远满载，没有一秒是等待。这才是真正的&nbsp;</span><b><span leaf=\"\">10x 工程师</span></b><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;的 Vibe。</span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"19\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016364\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5324675324675324\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2002\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=df86de82&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVCPUcu9nHoCpPIoqODk54sia4xfibqactLKd3ibROGe2rZUf8uNqbt3ED2g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">至于为啥需要用飞书写、还要讨论？ 可以参考我之前的文章</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&amp;mid=2247498637&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=dff471a4f5c9c3ea3cd892e4279cdca5&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"Claude Code极简入门：3条铁律让你告别代码屎山\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">Claude Code极简入门：3条铁律让你告别代码屎山</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 21px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: -0.003em;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;margin: 32px 0px !important;color: rgb(36, 36, 36) !important;line-height: 1.58 !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 32px 0px !important;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(36, 36, 36) !important;font-family: -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 21px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: -0.003em;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;line-height: 1.58 !important;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">六、数字保洁</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">例如 ——&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">整理笔记</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">整理电脑桌面</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">清理浏览器Tab</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">给微信新加的人打标签。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">给Logseq/Obsidian/Notion新写的笔记打标签。</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016365\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5516194331983806\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1976\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=084cd1f7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVCQOYI914M5wl9Tud1XroxlKMrb5cLoVhn8bxwJVRSavo1RvCDPINEQQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n   <p style=\"padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 21px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: -0.003em;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;margin: 32px 0px !important;color: rgb(36, 36, 36) !important;line-height: 1.58 !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 32px 0px !important;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(36, 36, 36) !important;font-family: -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 21px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: -0.003em;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;line-height: 1.58 !important;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">七、冥想 or 神游 or 呼吸</span></span></p>\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;list&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ul&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;list-style-type: circle;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;list-paddingleft-1&quot;,&quot;start&quot;:null},&quot;listitem&quot;,{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">闭眼，深呼吸1分钟，什么都不想。</span>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;list&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ul&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;list-style-type: circle;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;list-paddingleft-1&quot;,&quot;start&quot;:null},&quot;listitem&quot;,{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">不要惧怕休息！</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;list&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ul&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;list-style-type: circle;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;list-paddingleft-1&quot;,&quot;start&quot;:null},&quot;listitem&quot;,{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">休息，是为了更好的工作。休息，是做大事的战略性投入！</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">有个叫“生理性叹息”的呼吸法，大家一定要试一下，斯坦福科学家背书的，专门治各种突发性焦虑。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你不会冥想，教你一个简单的 ——&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\">斯坦福那个很火的神经科学家 Huberman，提过一个专门用来极速减压的招数，叫“生理性叹息（Physiological Sigh）”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">步骤特别简单，记住了： 鼻吸两下，口呼一下。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一下吸满，第二下补一口短的（把肺撑开），然后用嘴长长地吐气。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">只要两三个回合，心率马上就能稳住。不管是开会前紧张，还是写代码写烦了，用这个方法，物理降温，瞬间回血。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016366\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5458207452165156\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1986\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ece9ecad&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVCcPx6PGak4AibZsicMjDJk8Yp3tojvRBlpUW6WhiaibnELE0PMibjCU3oa8w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 21px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: -0.003em;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;margin: 32px 0px !important;color: rgb(36, 36, 36) !important;line-height: 1.58 !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.003em; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; margin: 32px 0px !important; color: rgb(36, 36, 36) !important; line-height: 1.58 !important;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">八、实体玩具</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">盘核桃、转笔、捏解压球、玩魔方。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我一般是转笔、玩魔方。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">毕竟我还没到盘核桃的年龄……</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">推荐魔方。因为魔方技术的上限很高。我在2016年专门练习了一下，最高记录可以20秒左右还原任意打乱的三阶魔方。（不计算预先观察和思考的时间）</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">玩魔方和写代码其实是一样的：</span><b data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">还原的过程，就是把混乱的熵减小为有序的过程。</span></b><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这或许就是程序员的本能吧。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你没玩过魔方，可能觉得20秒很快。其实并不快。目前世界纪录应该是3秒左右，而北京市海淀区的小学生魔方比赛，冠军也常常在6秒以内。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">总之，很有趣，你试试吧。 B站有很多魔方教程。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016367\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2010\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a21431ae&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVCxBwSc3EnFZOYLoPISm5CDhMEC3kAHJ6xLylJkbHq90YqeJDtsCPCYQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">九、疯狂切屏党</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">疯狂切屏党，也是一个老外常见的流派，它们叫做The \"Context Switchers\"。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">无论是Macbook还是Windows电脑，都支持多屏幕。只是很多人还没用过这个功能。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">据我所知，我的徒弟林悦己就是典型的“疯狂切屏党”。每次我看她电脑，我都觉得眼花缭乱。她似乎是每个屏幕都有不同用途。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"林悦己AI出海\" data-alias=\"V18102530370\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/0HvAIwdiaSMo3F0WXLo8ibGpicYPHngxYS8X2RVrTOgJpUuUJyhYaCJGIEUWCIumXK6GsiaIk4W3fu4iaIXtpvfkibRA/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"0基础转行🌊小白出海！vibe coding💻代表人物💰9天项目完成变现闭环🧠持续分享AI创业心酸史🔧让AI帮自己打工\" data-id=\"MzU2MTkyNzg4OQ==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">她有时候在写笔记、有时候在写Twitter、有时候在写复盘、有时候在逛淘宝…… 具体干啥不重要，设置还可以啥也不干，就切着玩也挺好玩的。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016368\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5486459378134403\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1994\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3bbf242f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVCgZ3cKicljjXaUTBDeD4BxiaxcUx3ZlWeCIo5CUWqNnrBoskSDRibXjRkA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n   <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">十、和AI聊天</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">和AI聊天，实际上是满足自己好奇心，是在学习。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016370\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.545\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2000\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=87da775f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVCicDPmjeVJ8N2iaXdVNJf5juiasibibIoWoFEL418I5z70UqLibKMa8XSic6Gg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我的朋友@亦仁 ，大概半年前，就发现自己使用ChatGPT的时间超过使用微信的时间了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我自己也有这个习惯，不过我一般不用手机，而是用电脑版。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016357\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"3.4203703703703705\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2d8c83e8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F607DKnuWzlEDAwenIbgAKp8DribQKstVCpuqX20O3mlBq90sBT3AF29tI93HHxrIhCod6Wmg8CreicZLHAXprzdw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">到底和哪个AI聊呢？要不要和ChatGPT聊呢？不一定，我是把三个AI大哥都同时订阅了$200美元/月或者$250美元/月的套餐，轮流玩。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近我发现和Gemini聊更好玩一点，因为Gemini 3有原生多模态，可以干到很多ChatGPT-5.2干不到的事，参考我这篇</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&amp;mid=2247499989&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=ea6543af1cd8266486800ff2ec342f7c&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"别被“多模态”骗了：用一本200页的教材，我测出了GPT-5.2和Gemini的物种代差\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">别被“多模态”骗了：用一本200页的教材，我测出了GPT-5.2和Gemini的物种代差</a></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">张一鸣用了那10秒思考出了今日头条的雏形。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">希望我们在Vibe Coding的这120秒里，也能找到属于我们的下一个“字节跳动”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">先分享到这里吧。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">你还有知道哪些Vibe Coding间隙适合干的事呢？期待分享！</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p>\n   <br>\n  </p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章分享了在 AI 代码生成等待时间中，技术人员如何有效利用碎片时间进行个人成长、效率提升和身心放松的十种实用方法，旨在变垃圾时间为价值时间，提高生产力。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章分享了在 AI 代码生成等待时间中，技术人员如何有效利用碎片时间进行个人成长、效率提升和身心放松的十种实用方法，旨在变垃圾时间为价值时间，提高生产力。",
  "summary": "本文围绕“等待 AI 写代码时我该干什么”这一核心问题，提出了十种利用 AI 生成代码的碎片化等待时间的有效活动。作者从张一鸣当年思考编译等待时间的轶事切入，强调了 AI 时代 Vibe Coding（氛围编程）的等待时间更具价值。建议的活动包括阅读电子书、与朋友聊天、写社交媒体（如公众号、Twitter）、微运动、深度编程（指令流水线思维）、数字保洁、冥想放松、玩实体玩具、疯狂切屏，以及与 AI 聊天学习。其中，深度编程部分强调在 PM、架构师、程序员角色间进行“纵向切换”，以提升效率。文章还结合了作者的个人实践和经验，提供了具体操作建议，旨在帮助技术从业者将 AI 等待时间转化为个人成长和效率提升的机会。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 生成代码的碎片化等待时间是宝贵的“高压输入”窗口，应高效利用。",
      "explanation": "在短暂的等待中，大脑因紧迫感进入高频吸收状态，适合阅读、思考，能有效摄取知识，实现知识的“静脉注射”提升学习效率。"
    },
    {
      "point": "采用“指令流水线”思维在 PM、架构师、程序员角色间纵向切换，可最大化深度编程效率。",
      "explanation": "在同一个项目内，同时进行需求编写、技术方案讨论和代码实现，避免项目间横向切换造成的“脑裂”，提高认知连续性和工作效率。"
    },
    {
      "point": "多种多样的小型活动可以有效填充 AI 等待时间，实现身心调节和成长。",
      "explanation": "包括阅读、社交、运动、数字管理、冥想、玩具体等，这些活动不仅能缓解工作压力，还能促进个人技能提升和身心健康，实现工作与生活的平衡。"
    },
    {
      "point": "社交媒体“Build in Public”对独立开发者具有重要价值。",
      "explanation": "通过公开分享开发过程和思考，独立开发者可以有效获取客户、与用户沟通，拓展个人影响力，实现商业获客。"
    },
    {
      "point": "“微运动”和“数字保洁”是利用碎片时间提升身心健康和工作效率的实用方法。",
      "explanation": "微运动可以缓解久坐带来的身体疲劳，数字保洁则能保持工作环境的整洁有序，减少认知负担，两者都有助于提升整体效率和幸福感。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "在程序编译的那 10 秒钟等待时间里，我到底应该干点什么？",
    "倒计时带来的隐形紧迫感，会强制你的大脑进入高频吸收状态。这不叫阅读，这叫知识的“静脉注射”。",
    "不要横向切换，要纵向切换。同一个项目，Cursor 写模块 A（现在），Claude 聊模块 B（马上做），飞书定义模块 C（未来做）。",
    "Build in Public 是一种很好的获取客户、和用户沟通的方式。",
    "还原的过程，就是把混乱的熵减小为有序的过程。这或许就是程序员的本能吧。"
  ],
